{"tid":1728674,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連儂 文宣 海外文宣 集中火力 - 二噁英","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T12:22:01.000Z","uid":49898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55ca9009a91108669cab1175b0bbab834ff0c7b9","tid":1728674,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"無論18區定海外文宣都好<br />\n集中火力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連儂牆同我清乾淨<br />\n</span></span><br />\n今日開始不斷重複貼<br />\n一幅牆一式一樣重覆<br />\n或者超大型超清晰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n二噁英對社區、對人類嘅影響<br />\n警隊亂放中国制有毒TG<br />\n政府一直都唔肯公開成分<br />\n有市民身體已有敏感反應<br />\n前線記者已出現中毒症狀<br />\n中毒後無法醫治<br />\n癌症<br />\n不育<br />\n生畸胎<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地之前搞咁多文宣<br />\n警暴 殺人 強姦 中共 政策 良知 民生<br />\n都好似無用<br />\n要歸邊嘅已一早歸邊<br />\n港豬藍屍根本無feel<br />\n覺得唔好搞到佢返工搵錢享受就咩都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n但二噁英問題係影響香港成個社區<br />\n佢地去邊都有機會直接接觸<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係會影響佢地身體 佢下一代健康同生育<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要俾佢知枝針已經拮到埋肉喇<br />\n港共係想毒死係香港嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n化學教授指出問題極嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F179179469403545%2Fposts%2F453229281998561%3Fvh%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=ad5ccaf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n立場匡哥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/503327553016621/posts/3072882642727753?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F503327553016621%2Fposts%2F3072882642727753%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=e13c1bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http